GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 14th November, 1956.
****
The undersigned is directed to inform Members of the
Council of Ministers that Shri Morarji R. Desai assumed office
as Cabinet Minister with effect from the forenoon of today, the
14 th November, 1956. He will hold charge of the Ministries of
Heavy Industries and Commerce & Consumer Industries.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy to:-
Asemie
(A.S. G111 )
for Secretary to the Cabinet.
